prodNameC: 鼻咽定康EB病毒核抗原IgG抗體檢驗試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Microelisa strip plate: Holder with 96 wells each coated with synthetic EBV EBNA-1 peptide.
Conjugate: HRP-labeled Anti-human IgG (goat).
Conjugate diluent: Phosphate buffer.
Calibrator I : Human serum containing 5 AU anti-EBNA IGg/ml (nonreactive level).
Calibrator II : Human serum containing 20 AU anti-EBNA IGg/ml (cut-off level).
Calibrator III : Human serum containing 110 AU anti-EBNA IGg/ml (reactive level).
Calibrator IV : Human serum containing 200 AU anti-EBNA IGg/ml (high reactive level).
Sample Diluent: Phosphate buffer.
Phosphate buffer concentrate: Concentrated (25x) phosphate buffer with 0.05% tween-20.
TMB substrate: Tetramethylbenziden and peroxide in citrate buffer.
Stop Solution: 0.2 mol/l sulfuric acid.
applicantName: 香港商生物梅里埃有限公司台灣分公司
applicantAddr: 台北市松山區南京東路5段34號4樓
efficacy: 利用ELISA方法測定人體血清或血漿中EBV EBNA IgG Ab.

mdKind.mdKindMCodeName: C 免疫學及微生物學用裝置
